00:16:53.839 --> 00:16:55.779
You cannot hide from rupture.

00:16:55.779 --> 00:16:57.350
Rupture will find you.

00:16:57.350 --> 00:17:03.990
Just like autumn then winter comes, you can’t
stop it and you don't want to stop it because

00:17:03.990 --> 00:17:06.459
if you do you won’t get spring.

00:17:06.459 --> 00:17:13.950
So it’s an interesting and magnificent way
for us to access who we are as women and who

00:17:13.950 --> 00:17:15.530
