00:18:01.790 --> 00:18:08.670
But the nature of the feminine is like a piano
with 88 keys.

00:18:08.670 --> 00:18:12.030
How boring would a piano be if it had one
key?

00:18:12.030 --> 00:18:17.310
And mostly women behave like they have one
key, middle C, and they just are like, “I’m

00:18:17.310 --> 00:18:18.310
fine.

00:18:18.310 --> 00:18:19.310
I’m fine.

00:18:19.310 --> 00:18:20.310
I’m fine.”

00:18:20.310 --> 00:18:27.170
And to really live what it means to be a woman,
you want to be a virtuoso of every facet of

00:18:27.170 --> 00:18:28.440
your emotional life.

00:18:28.440 --> 00:18:34.220
You want to experience the beautiful thrilling
little tinkling notes of joy and you want

00:18:34.220 --> 00:18:37.850
that pounding beautiful dark sorrow.

00:18:37.850 --> 00:18:44.720
In fact, the degree to which you can own your
light is only the degree to which you can

00:18:44.720 --> 00:18:46.210
