00:21:06.190 --> 00:21:11.950
makes room for you to stand for yours and
it spreads rather than spreading this virulent

00:21:11.950 --> 00:21:17.570
condition of self hate woman to woman, mother
to daughter all over this planet, which is

00:21:17.570 --> 00:21:19.540
what happens currently.

00:21:19.540 --> 00:21:27.470
We have the potential now to spread the virulent
condition of self love by taking a stand for

00:21:27.470 --> 00:21:30.590
